50|$|Thiopropazate (Artalan, Dartal, Dartalan, Dartan) is {{a typical}} {{antipsychotic}} of the phenothiazine class. It is a prodrug to <b>perphenazine.</b>|$|E
50|$|<b>Perphenazine</b> may {{increase}} the insulin needs of diabetic patients. Monitor blood glucose levels of insulin-dependent patients regularly during long-term treatment.|$|E
